# Squad Dashboards

## Dominio

Paineis configuraveis: dashboards com cards de graficos/KPIs, query engine dinamica por data source, filtros globais, layout grid drag-and-drop.

**Fonte de verdade:** PLANO.md secoes 1.5d (models Dashboard, DashboardCard, DashboardFilter), 2.6d (endpoints), Tela Paineis
**Fase PLANO:** F4C (construcao) + ownership continuo

